Say '''Loon''' et kumadwa ya klase baley ed luyag na [[Bohol]], [[Pilipinas]]. Unong ed 2010 Census, say papulasyon to et 42,800 totoo. Walay kabaleg tan sukat to ya 113.36 sq. km. Sikato et walad unaan ya distrito. Say zip code to et 6316.	
															
